4. Exercise for the Vibrato in
the Third Position.

Beginning with the third position
it becomes necessary to support the
left hand against the ribs and edge
of the belly (+). .However, when
the vibrato is employed in the higher
positions the hand must be held
away from the violin, so as not to
shake the instrument (*).

